The paper deals with the capacity region of a wireless communication system, specifically the Interference Channel with a Cognitive Relay (IFC-CR). This falls under the Information Theory (cs.IT) sub-category. Additionally, the paper discusses the use of a cognitive relay, which is related to the field of Network Intelligence (cs.NI). The paper also presents numerical evaluations, which could fall under Multimedia (cs.MM) or Computer Engineering (cs.CE). Finally, the paper discusses the capacity region of the interference channel, which is related to Signal Processing (cs.SP). However, since the focus is on the cognitive relay, it is less likely to be classified under cs.SP.
